---
---

<section class="section" style="background: var(--off-white);" aria-labelledby="apart-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="apart__layout">

      <div class="apart__left reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our approach</p>
        <h2 id="apart-heading">One platform.<br />Total mastery.</h2>
        <div class="accent-bar"></div>
        <p class="apart__lead">
          Most marketing agencies treat LinkedIn as one checkbox on a long list of channels.
          We treat it as the only one. That focus makes everything we do sharper and more
          accountable than what a generalist agency can offer.
        </p>
        <p class="apart__body">
          We know how the LinkedIn algorithm rewards consistency. We know which ad formats perform
          at each stage of the B2B funnel. We know what makes a B2B buyer stop scrolling, read,
          and act. We know because LinkedIn is all we do, every day.
        </p>
        <p class="apart__body">
          Strategy, platform audit, and performance reporting come with every engagement —
          not sold as extras.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="apart__pillars" aria-label="Core advantages">
        <div class="apart__pillar reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <span class="apart__pillar-num">01</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="apart__pillar-title">LinkedIn-only depth</h3>
            <p>Every recommendation is grounded in current mechanics, product updates, and B2B audience behaviour on LinkedIn specifically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="apart__pillar reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <span class="apart__pillar-num">02</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="apart__pillar-title">Global client base</h3>
            <p>We work with B2B companies from established multinationals to high-growth challengers, across industries and markets worldwide.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="apart__pillar reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <span class="apart__pillar-num">03</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="apart__pillar-title">Everything included</h3>
            <p>Strategy, platform audit, and performance reporting are part of every engagement. Not upsells. Not extras.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .apart__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .apart__lead {
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);
  }
  .apart__body {
    font-size: var(--fs-base);
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
  }

  .apart__pillars {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    padding-top: var(--sp-2);
  }

  .apart__pillar {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--sp-5);
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: var(--sp-6) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .apart__pillar:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .apart__pillar-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--blue);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 4px;
    min-width: 28px;
  }

  .apart__pillar-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-2);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .apart__pillar p {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .apart__layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--sp-10); }
  }
</style>
